name: SupportSethFranzC
_source: s;Seth;Franz. How are you holding up?
s;Franz;Fine. I may be young, but I'm every bit a Knight of Renais.|I'll fight to the end to protect the princess, just like you, sir!
s;Seth;Good, good! That's the spirit!|You know, you're looking much improved from when we set out.
s;Franz;Hm. Do you really think so, General?
s;Seth;Oh, definitely. You seem much more sure of yourself. All doubt has left your face.|By the time you reach my age, you'll be the finest spear- and swordsman around.
s;Franz;Honestly? Sir, do you really believe that?
s;Seth;...I do... But we are in a battle right now, Franz.|Concentrate on the enemies before you, and don't get too cocky.
s;Franz;Yes, sir!!!|You know I'd never let you down, sir!
s;Seth;Don't be too eager for success. Know your limits.
